<p>The last feature of the <em>student performance</em> page is a list of any recent comments the student has made in the forums for the class discussion group. (This only appears if you are looking at a <em>student performance</em> page for one of your own classes, since you cannot join discussions for another teacher&#8217;s class.)</p>
